metadata.name: Root
metadata.description:
"Root" is a digital version of oil painting on paper. The monochrome colour palette is used based on blue colour.

Artist tries to question the search for existential parts in the human soul by basing her works on the concepts of self-awareness, identity and self.

2480 x 3508 px
300 dpi

1 / 1 Edition

"Root", oil on paper
29 x 21 cm
2021
